  "aboutHeading": "Three decades of craftsmanship in Sonoma County",
  "aboutBody": [
    "DiFranco Gate & Fence Company is a residential and commercial automated gate, fence, and deck contractor with over 30 years of professional experience serving Sonoma County. Owner-operated by Mike DiFranco (CSLB #594909), the company has built its reputation on excellence and craftsmanship, developing lasting relationships with homeowners and contractors across the region.",
    "From custom automated entry gates and hand-fabricated ornamental iron to wood, bamboo, and vineyard fencing and redwood decks, every project is designed to beautify and enhance your property. DiFranco serves Sebastopol, Santa Rosa, Petaluma, Rohnert Park, Windsor, Healdsburg, Graton, Occidental, Forestville, and Guerneville."
  ],
  "servicesHeading": "What we build",
  "services": [
    {
      "title": "Custom automated gates",
      "description": "Custom-designed and hand-built automatic driveway gates — swing, slider, and solar-powered systems — with reliable, well-built security that adds value and elegance to your property."
